Imposition of a school uniform or dress code The document will discuss the pros and cons of students wearing a school uniform or adhering to a dress code. A relevant document will report on the value or positive gains in schools which have a school uniform or dress code in terms of department and educational gains, positive gains, i.e., less crime and better scholastic achievement in schools which have recently adopted a uniform/dress code.  Alternatively the article could discuss the negative effects of school uniforms or dress codes.
